<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Search Page</title>
    <script src="/static/cs.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .about-us-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-us-container h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-us-container h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .about-us-container p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 style="font-size:100%; padding:5px;text-align: center;">Search the News Feed</h1>
    <div class="nav-section nav-center" style="gap: 0.5rem; width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; box-sizing: border-box;">
        <form id="searchForm" class="search-form" style="flex: 1; display: flex; gap: 0; height: 40px; max-width: 555px;">
            <input type="text" id="searchInput" placeholder="Search" class="search-input" style="flex: 1; font-size: 1rem; padding: 0 1rem; outline: none; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 3.1rem 0 0 3.1rem; box-sizing: border-box;">
            <button class="nav-button search-button" type="submit" style="width: auto; padding: 0 1.25rem; border-radius: 0 3.1rem 3.1rem 0; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-left: 0;">Search</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div id="originalContent" class="about-us-container">
        <h1>News</h1>
        <h2>New Semester Begins on September 1st, 2024</h2>
        <p>The new academic year at XYZ University is set to begin on September 1st, 2024. All students are requested to complete their course registrations and prepare for an exciting year of learning and growth.</p>

        <h2>University Library Extends Hours During Exam Week</h2>
        <p>In preparation for the upcoming exam week, the university library will extend its hours from 8 AM to midnight starting next Monday. Students are encouraged to utilize this time for their studies and make the most of the available resources.</p>

        <h2>New Research Grant Available for STEM Students</h2>
        <p>XYZ University is pleased to announce a new research grant for students in the STEM fields. The grant will provide funding for innovative research projects that aim to address global challenges. Applications are open until October 15th, 2024.</p>

        <h2>Campus Security Upgraded with New Surveillance Systems</h2>
        <p>The university has upgraded its campus security with the installation of new surveillance systems. This initiative is part of our ongoing efforts to ensure the safety and security of all students and staff members.</p>

        <h2>Workshop on Digital Marketing to be Held Next Week</h2>
        <p>The Business Department is organizing a workshop on Digital Marketing for all interested students. The workshop will cover the latest trends and strategies in the field. It will be held on September 10th, 2024, in the Main Auditorium.</p>

        <h2>Alumni Meet Scheduled for November 2024</h2>
        <p>The annual Alumni Meet will take place in November this year. Alumni from all over the world are invited to reconnect with their peers and share their professional journeys with current students. More details will be shared soon.</p>
    </div>    

    <script>
        const originalContent = document.getElementById('originalContent').innerHTML;

        document.getElementById('searchForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            let searchQuery = document.getElementById('searchInput').value.toLowerCase();
            let container = document.getElementById('originalContent');
            container.innerHTML = ''; // Clear the current content

            if (searchQuery.trim() === '') {
                container.innerHTML = originalContent; // Restore the original content if the search is empty
                return;
            }

            let h2Elements = container.querySelectorAll('h2');
            let found = false;

            h2Elements.forEach(function(h2) {
                let p = h2.nextElementSibling;
                let h2Text = h2.textContent.toLowerCase();
                let pText = p.textContent.toLowerCase();

                if (h2Text.includes(searchQuery) || pText.includes(searchQuery)) {
                    found = true;
                    container.innerHTML += `<h2>${h2.innerHTML}</h2><p>${p.innerHTML}</p>`;
                }
            });

            if (!found) {
                container.innerHTML = `<p>"${searchQuery}" was not found.</p>`;
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
